<problem id="fs-idm385536896">
<para id="fs-idm388527264"><link class="lo-reference" document="m68073"/>Acme Inc. has the following information available:</para>
<media id="fs-idm374249552" class="scaled-down" alt="Actual price paid for material $1.00. Standard price for material $0.90. Actual quantity purchased and used in production 100. Standard quantity for units produced 110. Actual labor rate per hour $15. Standard labor rate per hour $16. Actual hours 200. Standard hours for units produced 220.">
